  "texts": [
    "If a perfect match is found, the corresponding Auslan gloss demonstration video from the database is retrieved and played.",
    "If no exact match is located, we provide similar English words in our database to the user's input.",
    "Subsequently, the corresponding Auslan gloss videos are provided to the user.",
    "This approach ensures that even if the exact word or phrase is not directly available, users can still access the most relevant Auslan gloss.",
    "It enhances the utility of the APP by accommodating variations in language and ensuring that users can effectively find and learn the Auslan equivalent of their textual input."
  ],
